flowchart TD
    A([Evaluate flag for user request]) --> B{Kill switch enabled?}
    B -- Yes --> C([Return: Feature OFF])
    B -- No --> D{User in allowlist?}
    D -- Yes --> E([Return: Feature ON])
    D -- No --> F{Evaluate targeting rules}
    F --> G{Any rule matches user attributes?}
    G -- Match found --> H[Return rule variant]
    H --> I([Return: Rule variant result])
    G -- No match --> J[Hash user ID to rollout bucket]
    J --> K{Bucket within rollout percentage?}
    K -- Within percentage --> L([Return: Feature ON])
    K -- Outside percentage --> M([Return: Feature OFF default])
